					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">To help debug your timing, run it in Nintendulator with Debugger, and set a breakpoint for CPU writes to 2005 or 2006.  Nintendulator is currently the only debugger which tells you the PPU clock value in addition to scanlines.
<br />If any PPU writes are outside the range of 256-341, you will get graphical glitches.</div>

					
